title: The Berenstain Bears Faithful Friends - Jan & Mike Berenstai
description:
The Berenstain Bears Faithful Friends (The Berenstain Bears Living Lights)
Author: Jan Berenstain & Mike Berenstain



This three-book collection of popular Berenstain Bears(r) Living Lights stories will provide children with an ideal gift they can enjoy all year long. The biblical values, morals, and life lessons are invaluable for children throughout every stage of their lives.

Titles include:

The Berenstain Bears Do Their Best, The Berenstain Bears Discover God's Creation & The Berenstain Bears Learn to Share"


Genre: Childrens
